text: Park Sun-mi (born November 22, 1972) is a South Korean taekwondo athlete and coach. Park Sun-mi won a gold medal at the 1994 Asian Taekwondo Championships in Manila and silver medal at the 1995 World Taekwondo Championships in Manila. Since the beginning of 2015 she is a head coach of Azerbaijani national female taekwondo team.Azərbaycan yığmalarının məşqçiləri təsdiqlənib ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean female taekwondo practitioners Category:Recipients of the Tereggi Medal Category:World Taekwondo Championships medalists Category:Asian Taekwondo Championships medalists
